en:
Language is a parasite residing within the human brain.
Haruhiko Ichijo, a summoner skilled in useless trivia and drawing;
Mai Kawakami, a martial artist constantly on the battlefield wielding the "Spirit of the Five Elements";
Reina Izumi, the legendary "Phantom Eater";
Koito Minase, a lone girl who controls sound like a porcelain doll.
Is this world real? Or is it an illusion?
